#: ../../benchmarks.md:1
msgid "Benchmarks"
msgstr "基准测试"

#: ../../benchmarks.md:3
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "总览"

#: ../../benchmarks.md:5
msgid ""
"Here is a quick overview of the execution time of Koffi calls on three "
"benchmarks, where it is compared to a theoretical ideal FFI "
"implementation (approximated with pre-compiled static N-API glue code):"
msgstr ""
"这里是Koffi在三个基准测试中的执行时间的概览, 对比的是理论上的理想FFI实现(以预编译的静态N-API胶水代码作为近似):"

#: ../../benchmarks.md:7
msgid "The first benchmark is based on `rand()` calls"
msgstr "第一个基准测试是基于调用`rand()`"

#: ../../benchmarks.md:8
msgid "The second benchmark is based on `atoi()` calls"
msgstr "第二个基准测试是基于调用`atoi()`"

#: ../../benchmarks.md:9
msgid "The third benchmark is based on [Raylib](https://www.raylib.com/)"
msgstr "第三个基准测试是基于[Raylib](https://www.raylib.com/)"

#: ../../benchmarks.md:18
msgid ""
"These results are detailed and explained below, and compared to node-ffi"
"/node-ffi-napi."
msgstr "下面有这些结果的详细信息和解释, 以及和node-ffi/node-ffi-napi的对比."

#: ../../benchmarks.md:20
msgid "Linux x86_64"
msgstr "Linux x86_64"

#: ../../benchmarks.md:22
msgid ""
"The results presented below were measured on my x86_64 Linux machine "
"(Intel® Core™ i5-4460)."
msgstr ""
"下面展示的结果是在我(@Koromix)的x86_64 Linux设备(Intel® Core™ i5-4460)上测试的."

#: ../../benchmarks.md:24 ../../benchmarks.md:70
msgid "rand results"
msgstr "rand结果"

#: ../../benchmarks.md:26 ../../benchmarks.md:72
msgid ""
"This test is based around repeated calls to a simple standard C function "
"atoi, and has three implementations:"
msgstr ""
#  "这个测试时基于持续调用一个简单的C函数atoi"

#: ../../benchmarks.md:28 ../../benchmarks.md:74
msgid ""
"the first one is the reference, it calls atoi through an N-API module, "
"and is close to the theoretical limit of a perfect (no overhead) Node.js "
"> C FFI implementation (pre-compiled static glue code)"
msgstr ""
"第一个是参考, 它通过一个N-API模块调用rand, 和理论上的最优(无开销)Node.js > C FFI实现(预编译静态胶水代码)接近."

#: ../../benchmarks.md:29 ../../benchmarks.md:75
msgid "the second one calls atoi through Koffi"
msgstr "第二个是通过Koffi调用atoi"

#: ../../benchmarks.md:30 ../../benchmarks.md:76
msgid "the third one uses the official Node.js FFI implementation, node-ffi-napi"
msgstr "第三个是使用官方的Node.js FFI实现, node-ffi-napi"

